							<font face="trebuchet ms,tahoma" size="3" color="#FFFFFF">Patch Day - Aug. 6th</b>
							<font face="trebuchet ms,tahoma" size="2" color="#FFFFFF"><br>
							Posted by <a target="_blank" href=/forum/pop_profile.asp?mode=display&id=218><font face="trebuchet ms,tahoma" size="2" color="#FFFFFF">Arathon Windmiller</a> On 08/06/2003 At  07:21:39 CST</font></a>
