							<font face="trebuchet ms,tahoma" size="3" color="#FFFFFF">Upcoming changes for Aug. 6th</b>
							<font face="trebuchet ms,tahoma" size="2" color="#FFFFFF"><br>
							Posted by <a target="_blank" href=/forum/pop_profile.asp?mode=display&id=218><font face="trebuchet ms,tahoma" size="2" color="#FFFFFF">Arathon Windmiller</a> On 07/30/2003 At  12:59:55 CST</font></a>
